@HostAddress = http://localhost:5292

### Route parameter - exact casing (expect 200)
GET {{HostAddress}}/hello/Active/world
Accept: application/json

###

### Route parameter - lowercase (expect 400 - the bug)
GET {{HostAddress}}/hello/active/world
Accept: application/json

###

### Route parameter - uppercase (expect 400 - the bug)
GET {{HostAddress}}/hello/ACTIVE/world
Accept: application/json

###

### Route parameter - non-enum segments case-insensitive (expect 200)
GET {{HostAddress}}/HELLO/Active/WORLD
Accept: application/json

###

### Query parameter - exact casing
GET {{HostAddress}}/query?status=Active
Accept: application/json

###

### Query parameter - lowercase
GET {{HostAddress}}/query?status=active
Accept: application/json

###

### Query parameter - uppercase
GET {{HostAddress}}/query?status=ACTIVE
Accept: application/json

###

